3. Privacy Policy
We take your data privacy seriously.

Location Data: We access your GPS coordinates and speed to overlay them on your videos. This data is only uploaded to our servers if you choose to "Share" or "Post" the video.

Data Storage: We use Google Firebase for secure data storage and authentication.

Data Deletion: You may delete your account and all associated data at any time via the "Settings" menu within the app.

Third Parties: We do not sell your personal data to third parties.